    "description": "Explore a region of <strong>mystery and danger</strong> in Ancient Mind, a modern take on the classic top-down <strong>puzzle-action adventure</strong>. Explore dungeons, fight <strong>monsters</strong>, solve <strong>puzzles</strong>, and discover the truth about ancient <strong>legends</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376750/extras/11f6b895b409a57d3e5912a9094f6379.avif?t=1762684197\" width=770 height=271 /></span><br><br>This game will put your <strong>spacial awareness</strong> to the test with a sequence of <strong>environmental puzzles</strong>, levels characterized by a non-linear structure made of <strong>keys and locks</strong>, dungeons full of <strong>monsters, traps, and riddles</strong>. Even with a map, you will still need to pay close attention to your surroundings and make a mental map of the area if you want to find your way to the end safe and sound.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376750/extras/483e2c720291b2684f4e4028b17aea79.avif?t=1762684197\" width=770 height=271 /></span><br><br>Ancient Mind is a modern take on the classic <strong>zelda-like</strong> top-down adventure. <strong>Fight monsters</strong> with your sword and use tools such as a <strong>grappling hook</strong> and torches to overcome obstacles and reach new areas. Items like <strong>bows and arrows</strong> are not only useful in combat, but also for triggering <strong>mechanisms</strong> in ancient temples. You will find new items as you progress into the game, unlocking paths even in already explored areas.<br><br>Sometimes, secret passages will only reveal themselves after you have acquired the necessary equipment or the necessary knowledge.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376750/extras/ba3caa957f07b534323a41b5148760f9.avif?t=1762684197\" width=770 height=271 /></span><br><br>Legends tell many stories about these lands, stories about an <strong>uncertain past</strong>. This region was once inhabited by an ancient civilization that now appears to have <strong>vanished</strong> into thin air, leaving behind nothing but ruins. Will you find the <strong>answers</strong> you're looking for? There might be <strong>clues</strong> behind every corner.<br><br>Collect information and ask the right questions as you explore the land, put the pieces together, and find out what happened in the past.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2376750/extras/f3d0a5fa9dd34db7facb6ae773f3c85d.avif?t=1762684197\" width=770 height=320 /></span>",
